OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784566087
OL,3,CCan Andy Burnham unite the country?
OL,5,FAs he enters No 10, Andy Burnham is at
OL,6,Fthe height of his power. So what do
OL,7,Fpeople want him to do with it?
OL,9,FWe've been delving into data shared
OL,10,Fwith us by More in Common to
OL,11,Funderstand people's priorities and the
OL,12,Fability of the new prime minister to
OL,13,Fconvince them that he has a plan.
OL,15,FThe top concern is abundantly clear `
OL,16,Fthe cost of living is cited by 70% of
OL,17,Fpeople as one of their main worries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
