CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784566087
OL,3,CCan Andy Burnham unite the country?
OL,5,FThat's followed by the NHS (30%) and
OL,6,Fimmigration (30%), so it's no surprise
OL,7,Fthat Burnham has decided to tackle the
OL,8,Fcost of living first.
OL,10,FBut do people think that he can
OL,11,Ftangibly improve their lives?
OL,13,FThere is evidence of increased
OL,14,Foptimism among the electorate of late.
OL,16,FWhen Labour first gained power in
OL,17,F2024, people thought that things would
OL,18,Fimprove ` 54% were hopeful.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784566087
OL,3,CCan Andy Burnham unite the country?
OL,5,FBut that dropped quite dramatically as
OL,6,FKeir Starmer's government bedded in `
OL,7,Ffalling to a low of around 26% of
OL,8,Fpeople who thought Labour would
OL,9,Fimprove their lives.
OL,11,FNow, it's begun to tick back up, with
OL,12,F41% feeling hopeful since it became
OL,13,Fclear that Burnham was going to be the
OL,14,Fnew prime minister.
OL,16,FHowever, how hopeful you feel depends
OL,17,Fquite significantly on where you live.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
