OL,3,CCan Andy Burnham unite the country?
OL,5,FIn the North West of England, where
OL,6,FBurnham was Mayor of Manchester until
OL,7,Frecently, 37% of people think he
OL,8,F'speaks for people' like them.
OL,10,FBut his reputation as 'King of the
OL,11,FNorth' over-simplifies the picture.
OL,13,FIn Yorkshire and the Humber, for
OL,14,Fexample, the figure falls to 23%.
OL,16,FThe 'North' (of England, let alone
OL,17,FScotland or Northern Ireland) is not
OL,18,Fsome homogenous block.
OL,20,FAnd the figure falls even more
OL,21,Fdramatically as you travel south.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
