OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784566087
OL,3,CCan Andy Burnham unite the country?
OL,5,FIn the South East of England, just 12%
OL,6,Fof people think that Burnham speaks
OL,7,Ffor them.
OL,9,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,10,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,11,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,12,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,14,FThat is a significant challenge, given
OL,15,Fthat Labour cannot rely solely on
OL,16,Fnorthern seats if it wants to win the
OL,17,Fnext general election.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
