OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784566087
OL,3,CCan Andy Burnham unite the country?
OL,5,FBurnham has stressed that he wants to
OL,6,Fbe a prime minister for north, south,
OL,7,Feast and west, but he still has some
OL,8,Fconvincing to do.
OL,10,FWe'll hear more from him in the coming
OL,11,Fdays and weeks and in reality, many
OL,12,Fvoters are yet to make up their minds.
OL,14,FThey need to know more before they
OL,15,Fgive an informed opinion. But Andy
OL,16,FBurnham doesn't have long.
OL,18,FPolitics moves fast these days, and he
OL,19,Fwill need to keep ahead of it if he's
OL,20,Fto buck the recent trend.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
